  "informal_statement": "The sum of all binomial coefficients choose(n,0) + choose(n,1) + ... + choose(n,n) equals 2^n, the total number of subsets of an n-element set.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Directly `Nat.sum_range_choose`.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem sum_range_choose' (n : ℕ) : (∑ m ∈ Finset.range (n + 1), Nat.choose n m) = 2 ^ n",
